org.dataconservancy.packaging.gui.view

Interface EditPackageContentsView

  • All Superinterfaces:
    View<EditPackageContentsPresenter>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    EditPackageContentsViewImpl

    public interface EditPackageContentsView
extends View<EditPackageContentsPresenter>
    A view that shows the pacakge description tree, and displays a popup to show package artifact properties. It will also display a popup if the package description isn't valid.
